#define R(p,a,t) mix(a*dot(p,a),p,cos(t))+sin(t)*cross(p,a)
#define H(h) (cos((h)*6.3+vec3(0,23,21))*.5+.5)

void mainImage(out vec4 O, in vec2 C)
{
    O=vec4(0);
	vec3 p,q,r=iResolution,
    d=normalize(vec3((C-.5*r.xy)/r.y,1));
    float i=0.,g=0.,e,s,t=iTime;
	for(;i++<99.;){
        p=d*g;
        p.xz-=mix(vec2(sin(t*.5),13.),vec2(1,7.),step(.7,fract(t*.3)));
        p+=i/1e3;
        p=R(p,normalize((H(t*.05)+sin(t*2.)*.1)*2.-1.),t*.2);
        e=s=2.;       
        p=abs(p)-2.5;
        p.x<p.z?p=p.zyx:p;
        p.y<p.z?p=p.xzy:p;
        p.x<p.y?p=p.yxz:p;
        s=2.;
        q=p*1.3;
        for(int j=0;j++<5;)
            p=1.-abs(p-1.),
            e=-5.*min(.6*max(1.2/dot(p,p),.8),1.),
            s*=abs(e),
            p*=e,
            p+=q,
            p=R(p,vec3(1,0,0),4.65);
        p.xy-=clamp(p.xy,-3.,3.);
        e=length(p.xy)/s;
        g+=e;
        O.rgb+=mix(vec3(1),H(log(s)*.2),.8)*.015/exp(i*i*e);
    }
}
